<h2>Why is the postage paid mailer no longer part of the package?</h2>
<p>
  Your participation in Preserve’s toothbrush recycling program has increased dramatically (nearly 400% growth) since the introduction of the Preserve Toothbrush in Mail-back Pack.  To sustain the program and to push recycling rates beyond the 20% mark, we have decided to take a new approach.  In order to get there, we need committed recyclers like you to recycle toothbrushes in bulk (starting with 2 at a time, and ideally 6 or more at a time).  This reduces costs and the amount of packaging used to send back the toothbrushes. Through this change we can recycle more and also reward you for recycling. Thank you for taking this step with us.
</p>

