<h2>How do I get rewards?</h2>
<p>
  Recycling is rewarding in and of itself, but to make this important action more fun we’re going to start offering you rewards. When you enter a unique rewards code to <a href="/return" title="Recycle Your Preserve Toothbrushes">recycle your toothbrush</a>, you will receive access to a big discount at our online store.   But this is only the first step. The more codes you enter, the more rewards we’ll send you (like free products). Stay tuned as more details will soon be announced.
</p>

